and she was just...

12:07.196 --> 12:08.996
Ugh! You know she's a snake oil
salesman, right?

12:09.065 --> 12:10.331
Yes, I know.

12:10.399 --> 12:11.999
People complain about
the diarrhea all the time,

12:12.018 --> 12:13.033
but that is the point.

12:13.102 --> 12:15.369
Her science is utter nonsense.

12:15.392 --> 12:17.359
I mean, space stickers
that give you energy,

12:17.428 --> 12:21.263
and crystals that absorb Wi-Fi,
and seriously... $1,200 socks?

12:21.332 --> 12:22.731
Those sheep eat nothing but sushi.

12:22.800 --> 12:25.500
- Are we done here?
- Surprisingly, not.

12:26.136 --> 12:28.003
This might sound crazy, but...

12:28.072 --> 12:30.201
- I'm going to marry you.
- What?!

12:30.226 --> 12:33.007
