by the way.

14:01.261 --> 14:03.094
- Those are for dogs.
- Oh, no.

14:03.163 --> 14:05.030
Ay, Phil, are you okay?

14:05.098 --> 14:06.398
Yeah, yeah.

14:06.466 --> 14:08.633
