daughter. I'll have to smother him, too.

14:34.275 --> 14:36.175
That's two pillows from the
same set. It's a pattern.

14:36.244 --> 14:38.911
- The police are after me!
- Get ahold of yourself!

14:38.980 --> 14:40.779
- Ay!
- Ow! What the hell?

14:40.893 --> 14:43.093
It wasn't me. Look, I'm still cocked!

14:43.162 --> 14:44.594
It was a shoe.

14:44.663 --> 14:46.163
Wait, that's...

14:46.231 --> 14:48.065
that's Luke's.

14:48.133 --> 14:49.399
LUKE: Hey!

14:49.468 --> 14:51.868
Luke! You're okay!

14:51.937 --> 14:53.837
I got stuck on the roof.

14:53.906 --> 14:55.505
I'm so relieved!

14:55.574 --> 14:57.707
I don't have to kill your mother!

14:58.811 --> 15:00.343
Turns out,
Luke had to go to the bathroom.

15:00.412 --> 15:01.678
Someone told him it was upstairs,

15:01.747 --> 15:03.080
so he walked all the way up to the roof

15:03.148 --> 15:04.614
and locked himself out.

15:04.683 --> 15:06.483
His phone was dead,
and he... he lost his voice

15:06.552 --> 15:08.919
