the street musicians.

15:08.987 --> 15:11.922
I was so relieved, I ran up there and
gave him a big kiss.

15:12.664 --> 15:14.598
PHIL: Gloria!

15:14.666 --> 15:16.399
Hi. We're stuck.

15:16.468 --> 15:19.102
Could you pop on up and open the door?

15:19.171 --> 15:20.837
Dunphy men.

15:24.543 --> 15:26.176
Hello, Lazlo.

15:26.245 --> 15:29.612
- It's pronounced "Lazlo".
- That's what I said.

15:29.757 --> 15:31.457
Thank you so much for meeting with us.

15:31.525 --> 15:33.125
Have you had a chance
to consider our offer

15:33.194 --> 15:34.326
