15:34.395 --> 15:36.829
I'm intrigued,
but I have a list of demands.

15:36.897 --> 15:39.498
Ah, yes, of course.

15:39.567 --> 15:40.833
We have, uh...

15:40.901 --> 15:43.102
...uh, "Two turquoise bowls
of white Chiclets,

15:43.170 --> 15:45.404
an empty office
with a drain in the floor..."

15:45.473 --> 15:47.773
- What's a "scream room"?
- I think that's self-explanatory.

15:47.842 --> 15:49.208
- Hmm.
- SHIRL: Pritchett!

15:49.276 --> 15:50.509
Girl Earl!

15:50.578 --> 15:54.446
You're actually trying
to poach Lazlo from me?

15:54.589 --> 15:55.955
I thought we were friends.

15:56.023 --> 15:58.157
We were, and then you bought
all my pineapple knobs.

15:58.226 --> 15:59.859
- As a gift!
- What?

15:59.927 --> 16:01.427
- I had them sent to you.
- You did?

16:01.495 --> 16:04.830
