16:54.679 --> 16:57.334
No, no, you do not get to have an
epiphany right now!

16:57.369 --> 16:59.058
I am furious at you!

16:59.093 --> 17:01.760
The answer is...yes.

17:02.617 --> 17:04.357
People say that NERP

17:04.425 --> 17:05.791
