from a kooky actress.

17:08.763 --> 17:09.996
Ugh.

17:10.065 --> 17:12.050
Oh, I'm sorry. Was that a question?

17:12.086 --> 17:13.184
- No.
- Oh, okay.

17:13.219 --> 17:14.219
But...

17:14.306 --> 17:15.659
